  <para>
    This document contains a brief manual for the <acronym>qdmr</acronym> graphical user interface 
    (<acronym>GUI</acronym>) application to program <acronym>DMR</acronym> radios. The aim of this 
    application is to provide a simple to use, platform and vendor independent and well documented 
    codeplug programming software (<acronym>CPS</acronym>) for popular <acronym>DMR</acronym> radios.
  </para>
